<template>
    <button @click="count++"><Thumbsupicon>t class = "src\assets\images\like_thumb.png" </Thumbsupicon> {{ count }}</button>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: "thumbsUp",
    data() {
    return {
      count: 0
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
button {
  font-weight: bold;
}
</style>
